APT - Finding Files in Packages

Use [prgm]apt-file[/prgm] to search for files across packages.

$ [prgm]apt-file search[/prgm] [arg-value]path[/arg-value]              # Find which package provides a file
$ [prgm]apt-file list[/prgm] [arg-value]package[/arg-value]             # List all files in a package

[dim]Requires installation and an initial [prgm]apt-file update[/prgm] to build the database.[/dim]
